171
00:13:46,220 --> 00:13:47,280
What's wrong?

172
00:13:47,410 --> 00:13:49,710
You look pretty stressed out lately.

173
00:13:50,020 --> 00:13:51,619
You could tell, huh?

174
00:13:51,620 --> 00:13:52,590
Of course.

175
00:13:54,380 --> 00:13:55,920
Nie Jitian

176
00:13:56,650 --> 00:13:58,950
had committed all kinds of evil deeds
for his selfish desires.

177
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:00,400
Even so, I couldn't arrest him.

178
00:14:01,260 --> 00:14:02,750
It's not that you couldn't arrest him.

179
00:14:02,770 --> 00:14:04,520
It's just that it isn't time yet.

180
00:14:04,690 --> 00:14:06,859
It's just like the slope we're taking right now.

181
00:14:06,860 --> 00:14:09,980
We cannot reach the top with one step,
not to mention arresting a criminal like him.

182
00:14:09,980 --> 00:14:10,800
Don't you agree?

183
00:14:13,260 --> 00:14:13,920
What's wrong?

184
00:14:13,930 --> 00:14:14,920
Wait for me.

185
00:14:19,140 --> 00:14:20,440
This is for you.

186
00:14:21,690 --> 00:14:23,379
I specifically went to Wong Tai Sin

187
00:14:23,380 --> 00:14:25,280
