perform a ritual to bless it.

188
00:14:26,380 --> 00:14:27,280
What is this?

189
00:14:27,770 --> 00:14:29,400
This is a charm of safety.

190
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:30,499
Remember,

191
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:32,470
do not remove it once you've put it on.

192
00:14:34,170 --> 00:14:37,560
In the future,
I won't be the only kin you have.

193
00:14:37,650 --> 00:14:39,160
You have another kin now.

194
00:14:40,980 --> 00:14:42,070
Dear,

195
00:14:43,290 --> 00:14:44,870
