Kaiqing,

200
00:15:08,380 --> 00:15:09,400
I've made a new discovery.

201
00:15:09,500 --> 00:15:11,379
When I checked the name list of the victims,

202
00:15:11,380 --> 00:15:12,619
there's a female college student

203
00:15:12,620 --> 00:15:13,529
called Lai Yingqiao.

204
00:15:13,530 --> 00:15:14,289
She might be

205
00:15:14,290 --> 00:15:15,160
Mai Zhihong's tutor.

206
00:15:15,170 --> 00:15:16,750
