207
00:15:22,260 --> 00:15:24,750
This isn't right.

208
00:15:25,020 --> 00:15:26,200
That's not it.

209
00:15:47,260 --> 00:15:48,689
Wait, this isn't right.

210
00:15:48,690 --> 00:15:50,990
You just had a close shave, you know?

211
00:15:52,530 --> 00:15:54,160
Now, you're still
investigating the case?

212
00:15:56,340 --> 00:15:58,960
You're visiting me this early in the morning.
Did you find any clues?

213
00:15:59,740 --> 00:16:00,680
Buddy,

214
00:16:01,140 --> 00:16:02,990
