for a criminal, you know?

215
00:16:03,050 --> 00:16:04,520
News of this has gotten out.

216
00:16:05,380 --> 00:16:05,859
A reporter

217
00:16:05,860 --> 00:16:07,400
wants to interview you.

218
00:16:07,930 --> 00:16:09,140
That's why I'm here to find you.

219
00:16:09,140 --> 00:16:10,110
Stop bothering me.

220
00:16:12,450 --> 00:16:13,710
I guessed it as much.

221
00:16:14,500 --> 00:16:17,020
In the past, you weren't willing
to make a public appearance

222
00:16:17,020 --> 00:16:18,470
no matter how huge the case was.

223
00:16:19,500 --> 00:16:21,595
However, there are certain things
that you cannot avoid.

224
00:16:22,260 --> 00:16:23,590
Our higher-up intends to visit you.

225
00:16:25,340 --> 00:16:26,160
You mean Officer Ma?

226
00:16:27,410 --> 00:16:28,400
That's right.

227
00:16:29,020 --> 00:16:31,070
He said he was most concerned about

228
00:16:31,170 --> 00:16:32,710
the safety of his colleagues.

229
00:16:34,740 --> 00:16:37,280
More like he's doing this
because he wants to be on camera.

230
00:16:37,450 --> 00:16:38,440
Stop bothering me.

231
00:16:40,380 --> 00:16:41,019
Don't worry.

232
00:16:41,020 --> 00:16:42,520
I'll reject the interview
on your behalf.

233
00:16:44,530 --> 00:16:45,640
I'll tell you the same thing.

234
00:16:48,650 --> 00:16:49,830
Stop investigating the case.

235
00:16:54,340 --> 00:16:55,200
I'll be leaving now.

236
00:16:59,530 --> 00:17:00,710
I'll do the interview.

237
00:17:03,260 --> 00:17:05,310
Hello, Officer Chen.
Thank you for accepting our offer.

238
00:17:05,340 --> 00:17:06,339
How's your body doing

239
00:17:06,340 --> 00:17:07,680
after getting shot?

240
00:17:08,730 --> 00:17:10,200
I'm lucky. I'll survive.

241
00:17:10,730 --> 00:17:11,680
Regarding this incident,

242
00:17:11,820 --> 00:17:12,984
people have divided opinions.

243
00:17:12,984 --> 00:17:16,059
Some netizens said you were silly for
blocking the bullet on the criminal's behalf.

244
00:17:16,060 --> 00:17:17,710
But some of them said you were a hero.

245
00:17:18,490 --> 00:17:19,790
Officer Chen, what's your opinion?

246
00:17:21,860 --> 00:17:24,449
This time, we took down the hitman.

247
00:17:24,450 --> 00:17:26,030
We also ensured
the safety of the witness.

248
00:17:26,540 --> 00:17:27,360
Actually,

249
00:17:27,650 --> 00:17:29,649
the actual unsung hero is my boss.

250
00:17:29,650 --> 00:17:30,539
He's my superior,

251
00:17:30,540 --> 00:17:31,270
Officer Ma.

252
00:17:31,540 --> 00:17:32,750
Officer Ma, please come here.

253
00:17:33,770 --> 00:17:35,570
Luckily, Officer Ma
made several backup plans.

254
00:17:35,570 --> 00:17:38,459
He notified me in time. If not,
we wouldn't have been able to stop the hitman.

255
00:17:38,459 --> 00:17:39,800
The consequences would've been dire.

256
00:17:39,800 --> 00:17:40,860
Dear friends from the media,

257
00:17:40,860 --> 00:17:43,450
I'm just in charge of
the strategy and deployment.

258
00:17:43,450 --> 00:17:47,009
Most importantly, this couldn't have worked without
the effort of my colleagues at the frontline.

259
00:17:47,009 --> 00:17:49,030
It wouldn't work out
if they didn't carry out my order.

260
00:17:49,030 --> 00:17:51,970
Officer Ma, most importantly,
your strategy and deployment was perfect. Right?

261
00:17:51,970 --> 00:17:52,750
You reinstated me.

262
00:17:54,500 --> 00:17:56,490
Officers, why don't you guys
take a picture together?

263
00:17:56,490 --> 00:17:57,160
Sure.

264
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:58,510
You can stand in the center, okay?

265
00:17:59,000 --> 00:17:59,969
Officer Ma, look here.

266
00:17:59,970 --> 00:18:01,209
Officer Ma, look at the camera.

267
00:18:01,210 --> 00:18:01,819
Look over here.

268
00:18:01,820 --> 00:18:02,969
